**Zsh:**
```bash
# Add to ~/.zshrc
eval "$(rch completion zsh)"

# Or save to fpath
rch completion zsh > ~/.zfunc/_rch
# Ensure ~/.zfunc is in fpath before compinit
```

**Fish:**
```bash
